As a sales user,
I want a sales force instance created with following screen tabs.

1. Customized Home page (with our company logo)
2. Accounts
3. Opportunites
4. Leads
5. Contacts
6. Campaigns

Each tab will have related object as follows.

Home page; Opportunity based summary report.
Accounts: Contacts, Opportunites,Cases, Notes & Attachments.
Opportunites: Products and Solutions, Support request (custom based on Case), Service Locations (custom), Design and Solutions (custom), Notes and Attachments
Leads: Activits (oob)
Contacts: OOB
Campaigns: OON

